//medium.com/the-harry-potter-alliance/demographics-and-research-d409be83538c</a><br>#LGBTQ #inclusivedesign","favorite_count":"5","retweet_count":"1"},{"created_at":"Fri May 17 02:58:04 +0000 2019","id_str":"1129219503093702657","full_text":"Looking forward to seeing everyone in Higashi-Gotanda tonight! @codechrysalis <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/ja-JP/CodeChrysalis/events/260904930/\">https://www.meetup.com/ja-JP/CodeChrysalis/events/260904930/</a>","favorite_count":"5","retweet_count":"2"},{"created_at":"Mon May 13 04:22:10 +0000 2019","id_str":"1127791118731493376","full_text":"I'll be having a session this Friday (the 17th) on designing for the LGBTQ community and the decisions we made with Hello!Rainbow to make our app #inclusive for the queer community in Tokyo! Come say hi!<br><br><a href=\"http://meetu.ps/e/GGxvv/JqX8Z/a\">http://meetu.ps/e/GGxvv/JqX8Z/a</a><br><br>#LGBTQ #tokyo #inclusivedesign","favorite_count":"8","retweet_count":"5"},{"created_at":"Thu May 09 09:01:57 +0000 2019","id_str":"1126411974831513600","full_text":"お願いします〜　#LGBTQ<br>#buzzfeedjapan<br><br><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bw1Wm6ihC7S/\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bw1Wm6ihC7S/</a>","favorite_count":"1","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Mon Apr 29 22:52:36 +0000 2019","id_str":"1122997138743595009","full_text":"Thanks to everyone who came out to #TokyoRainbowPride! We’re @apphellorainbow, a social app for LGBTQ folks to meet other queer friends in Tokyo. Come try out our prototype here and give us feedback: <a href=\"https://www.hellorainbow.app\">https://www.hellorainbow.app</a>","favorite_count":"4","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Wed Apr 24 04:35:41 +0000 2019","id_str":"1120909149435387904","full_text":"It’s the ideal right? Finding people who share things you like that you feel like “get” you at the very beginning? We created @apphellorainbow for that purpose.","favorite_count":"0","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Wed Apr 24 04:35:41 +0000 2019","id_str":"1120909148093210624","full_text":"You’re gay, living with your partner and you like sports? You deserve a pick-up soccer group that doesn’t ask you how your wife is.<br><br>You’re trans and like DnD? You deserve a DnD group where you can swap presentation tips while battling demons.","favorite_count":"1","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Wed Apr 24 04:09:55 +0000 2019","id_str":"1120902666832400384","full_text":"If you’re looking for a queer friend-making app that has the best, cutest pins, look no further than @apphellorainbow. Come visit us at #trp2019 both days at booth 204! #tokyorainbowpride #queer #LGBTQ <div class=\"gallery\"><ul><li><a href=\"../../tweets_media/1120902666832400384-D44_Ax2U8AAkyXM.jpg\"><img src=\"../../tweets_media/1120902666832400384-D44_Ax2U8AAkyXM.jpg\"></a></li></ul></div>","favorite_count":"5","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Wed Apr 24 01:54:06 +0000 2019","id_str":"1120868486060732427","full_text":"If you want to follow our progress on social media with Hello!Rainbow, please follow @apphellorainbow on Twitter or hellorainbowapp on insta: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hellorainbowapp/\">https://www.instagram.com/hellorainbowapp/</a><br><br>&lt;3<br>#LGBT #TRP2019 #tokyo","favorite_count":"1","retweet_count":"0"},{"created_at":"Mon Apr 22 05:12:49 +0000 2019","id_str":"1120193718223425537","full_text":"Come to #TRP2019 and try out our new prototype for making queer friends in Tokyo! ハローレインボーという東京でLGBTQ友達を作るソーシャルアプリが配信開始！２０４号ブースでお待ちしております〜 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hellorainbowx/status/1120192572855439361\">https://twitter.com/hellorainbowx/status/1120192572855439361</a>","favorite_count":"4","retweet_count":"3"},{"created_at":"Fri Apr 12 06:33:32 +0000 2019","id_str":"1116590152061607938","full_text":"Huge thanks to @richdecibels for spelling out this awesome framework for balancing power dynamics.<br><br><a href=\"https://medium.com/the-tuning-fork/11-practical-steps-towards-healthy-power-dynamics-at-work-fcc9bd82c7a2\">htt